	(text "- Cs >> Cx must be observed for proper operation.\n- Load capacitance (Cx) ranges from 5-20pF while Cs is usually about 2-50 nF.\n- Decreasing Cs will reduce sensor gain.\n- High values of Cx will reduce sensor gain.\n- Keep ground away from the electrodes and traces and IC."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 135.636 73.66 0)
		(effects
